{"tid":1563159,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"近九成教協會員指政治壓力源自政府 四成源自何君堯","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:39:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8128221bb10df102a39a96af661565f0045c46d6","tid":1563159,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"近期反修例事件中，社會上不同人士或會受到政治壓力，教協於本月9日至12日對所有中小學和特殊學校任教的教協會員進行調查，並收回668份回覆。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">有87.4%受訪者認為政府及教育局給予他們政治壓力</span>，當中更有52.7%指有非常大壓力是來自政府和教育局。另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">有76.8%指「其他教育界以外人士」令他們感到政治壓力，而近四成主動指立法會議員何君堯是政治壓力來源</span>。<br />\n<br />\n相反，<span style=\"color: red;\">調查認為由學生造成有點壓力的只有36.7%</span>，教協認為結果反映政治壓力來源並不是主要來自學生示威活動本身，而是校外人士的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n教協強烈要求政府、教育局和部分建制派議員，立即停止向學校施加政治壓力，給予學校足夠喘息空間，以教育專業去處理校內事務。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2249143/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2249143%2F&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb%2BCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=034a3cb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2249143/</a>"},{"pid":"33e572734d6aee5314106235a6b57d0dd7dacdd2","tid":1563159,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: